    "description": "This Grasshopper plugin integrates the IfcOpenShell library directly into Rhino and Grasshopper, enabling users to work with Industry Foundation Classes (IFC) files within their parametric design workflows. The plugin provides a comprehensive toolkit for importing, inspecting, editing, and exporting BIM data using the open IFC standard.",
